  "prompt": "Fix this code.\n\nGoal:\nGroup events into sessions per user.\nA new session starts if the time gap is greater than 10.\nAn exact gap of 10 stays in the same session.\n\nReturn:\nuser -> list of sessions\neach session is a list of event ids\n\n```python\ndef group_sessions(events):\n    sessions = {}\n    last_time = {}\n\n    for user, event_id, timestamp in events:\n        if user not in sessions:\n            sessions[user] = []\n            sessions[user].append([])\n\n        if user in last_time:\n            if timestamp - last_time[user] >= 10:\n                sessions[user].append([])\n\n        sessions[user][-1].append(event_id)\n        last_time[user] = timestamp\n\n    return sessions\n```\n\nReturn only code.",
